# Uncomment the next line to ignore ALL data dirs by default:
# **/Data/

# Generated report figures under */Output/ are intentionally COMMITTED (not
# ignored) so the project READMEs render results on GitHub without running the
# code. They're deterministic (fixed random_state), so they change only when the
# code does. Ignore an Output/ dir here if a project's figures get large.

# ---- Notebooks: strip heavy outputs before committing when possible ----

